  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/417a69f19e4fad84356ae09a3fed5331.poster.avif?t=1703068280\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/417a69f19e4fad84356ae09a3fed5331.webm?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/417a69f19e4fad84356ae09a3fed5331.mp4?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>97 choices. 28 endings.<br>Do you think you can experience a life with game?<br>It is possible if you make a number of cases.<br>The number of cases in the interactive game “Yeon-oh and Seo” is 4656.<br>Let's start a new life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Synopsis]</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/54b921315ec6994e931de39f1ca96c44.poster.avif?t=1703068280\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/54b921315ec6994e931de39f1ca96c44.webm?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/54b921315ec6994e931de39f1ca96c44.mp4?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>“Hey, you couple over there! Please keep it down at campus.”<br>Yeon-Oh and Seo, A famous couple represents Pohang University of Science and Technology graduating class.<br>'Yeon-oh' runs a robot startup and 'Seo' is an outsider engineering student and s theater director.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/f25d31141e94ac032a3b3cdb52e239fe.poster.avif?t=1703068280\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/f25d31141e94ac032a3b3cdb52e239fe.webm?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/f25d31141e94ac032a3b3cdb52e239fe.mp4?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"Yeon-oh! Our investment is confirmed!\"<br>Yeon-oh is a university student and the CEO of , a startup which makes robots.<br>He started a humble business with his friends, but finally he received an investment offer from a conglomerate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/b08ac6eae01cd1e9c3ac6c0c277efe5c.poster.avif?t=1703068280\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/b08ac6eae01cd1e9c3ac6c0c277efe5c.webm?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/b08ac6eae01cd1e9c3ac6c0c277efe5c.mp4?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>“Seo, Would it be okay as we are now?”<br>Yeon-oh accepts the investment proposal and plans to go to Seoul.<br>Seo decides to stay in Pohang to run a theater company which is her dream.<br>Soon numerous temptations and conflicts bock their way.<br>All of this is up to your choice.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/c9e6fda0d51d833d112b2475608fa9d2.poster.avif?t=1703068280\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/c9e6fda0d51d833d112b2475608fa9d2.webm?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/c9e6fda0d51d833d112b2475608fa9d2.mp4?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If we had made a different choices back then, what would we be like now?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/14b18777a00b07c33c131b8bb515da4f.poster.avif?t=1703068280\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/14b18777a00b07c33c131b8bb515da4f.webm?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/14b18777a00b07c33c131b8bb515da4f.mp4?t=1703068280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Select a character<br>When the prologue starts, choose one character between 'Yeon-oh and Seo'.<br>If you choose Yeon-oh, the events will proceed from Yeon-oh's point of view, and if you choose Seo, events will proceed from Seo's point of view.<br>The story of “Yeon-oh” and the story of “Seo” are organically linked.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353380/extras/a8ddc1ec4a55ed3ace3f63dcb4220672.avif?t=1703068280\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>2. Select the character's action or answer through the button that pops up at each turning point.<br>Those choices come together and determine their future.<br>If you don't like a choice or ending, you can get back to another selection in the past.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game characteristics</h2>1. The player creates the story and the ending making 97 choices<br>2. Organic linkage of stories for each character<br>3. Nonlinear multiple endings with thousands of cases and endings<br>4. Multi-time play",
